{"product_id":"madara-moonlight-soft-glow-mineral-highlighter-1-stardust","title":"MÁDARA Moonlight Soft Glow Mineral Highlighter, #1 Stardust 6g","description":"\u003cp\u003eWhile nothing beats the magical glow of moonlit skin, this natural highlighter comes delightfully close. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003eInfused with ultra-refined, light-reflecting mineral particles, it delivers a soft, iridescent finish that looks just like your skin — only more luminous. The talc-free formula with skin-loving ingredients blends effortlessly, adapting to your skin’s texture. Suitable for fair to medium skin. \u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eSweep onto the high points of your face — cheekbones, brow bones, bridge of the nose and cupid’s bow — using a brush or fingertips. Blend gently for a soft glow or layer for a more intense radiance. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e MICA (CI 77019)**; LAUROYL LYSINE; ZINC STEARATE; SILICA; CAPRYLIC\/CAPRIC TRIGLYCERIDE; LECITHIN; CAPRYLYL GLYCOL; TOCOPHEROL; ARGANIA SPINOSA (ARGAN) KERNEL OIL*; GLYCINE SOJA (SOYBEAN) OIL*; AROMA; CERA ALBA (BEESWAX)*; MAGNESIUM STEARATE; AQUA; GLYCERIN; POLYGLYCERYL-3 DIISOSTEARATE; GLYCOLIPIDS; ORYZA SATIVA (RICE) EXTRACT; ORYZA SATIVA (RICE) GERM EXTRACT; ASCORBYL PALMITATE; LINALOOL***; GERANIOL***; GERANYL ACETATE***; VANILLIN; CI 77891 (TITANIUM DIOXIDE) **; CI 77491 (IRON OXIDES)**; CI 77492 (IRON OXIDES)**; CI 77499 (IRON OXIDES)**\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e*Ingredients from organic farming\u003cbr\u003e**Pure mineral pigments\u003cbr\u003e***From natural essential oils\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e100% Natural origin of total\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"productPage-ingredientMessage-3FP\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"richContent-root-3Sy\"\u003ePlease note that ingredient lists may change and slightly vary from time to time. You will always find the most up-to-date information on the actual product packaging.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"richContent-root-3Sy\"\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCOSMOS NATURAL certified\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"MADARA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":52634465141063,"sku":null,"price":24.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/madara-moonlight-soft-glow-mineral-highlighter-1-stardust-6g-4312432.jpg?v=1762389188","url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/products\/madara-moonlight-soft-glow-mineral-highlighter-1-stardust","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}